This is based on moodle-offline-grading by Andy Sayler:
https://github.com/asayler/moodle-offline-grading


Tools for running grading scripts on Canvas assignments

OVERVIEW:

    These tools provide a basic framework for mapping an auto-grading
    script across a set of Canvas submissions.


